        </listApp>
      </div>
      <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation">
        <p n="1-2">Tenth year of the victorious king Kampavikramavarman.</p>
        <p n="2-7">When the army of Pirutikaṅkaraiyar was stationed <supplied reason="explanation">
            <foreign>nikka</foreign>
            <note>That is, <foreign>nīkka</foreign>?</note>
          </supplied> <supplied reason="subaudible">in</supplied> Kāvaṉṉūr in the Mīyārunāṭu in the Paṭuvūrkkōṭṭam, Perunakar koṇṭa Kāviti<note>That is, "the minister who took Perunakar".</note>, a soldier of Vāṇaraiyar<note>That is, "the Bāṇa king".</note>, having ... fell.</p>
      </div>
